<HEAD>&para;The fourth chapitre of the fourth book Is of the ys|suynge of the Alphyn.</HEAD>
<P>THe manere <ABBR>and</ABBR> nature of the draught of the Al+phyn is suche / that he that is black in his propre siege is sette on the right side of the kynge / <ABBR>And</ABBR> he that is whyt is sette on the lifte side / <ABBR>And</ABBR> ben
