<DIV2 N="5" TYPE="chapter">
<HEAD>&para;The fyfth chapitre of the fourth Tractate Is of the meuynge of the knyghtes.</HEAD>
<P>AFter the yssue of the Alphyns we <ABBR>shall</ABBR> deuyse to yow the yssue &amp; the moeuynge of the knygh|tes / <ABBR>And</ABBR> we saye that the knyght on the right syde is whyt / <ABBR>And</ABBR> on the lifte syde black / <ABBR>And</ABBR> the yssue <ABBR>and</ABBR> moeuynge of hem bothe is in one maner whan so is that the knyght on the ryght syde Is whyt / The lyfte knyght is black / The moeuynge of hem is suche / That the whyte may goo in to the space of the alphyn / as hit apperyth of the knyght on the right side that is whyte.
